=== Etymology ===
*[[仏]] (ふつ, ''futsu'') which is an abbreviation for 仏蘭西(ふらんす, ''furansu'') (''France'') + [[語]] (ご, ''go'') (''language'')(1.)
*[[仏]] (ぶつ, ''butsu'') (''Buddha'') + [[語]] (ご, ''go'') (''words'')(2.)
